data.description: Location, location, location! Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this traditional 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home located in the sought-after Leon Valley, just outside the Medical Center. With an open floor plan that seamlessly connects living spaces, this residence offers an inviting atmosphere for families and gatherings. The heart of the home lies in the island kitchen, adorned with granite countertops and 42-inch cabinets, combining functionality and style for culinary enthusiasts. The spacious bedrooms provide ample privacy, and the master suite offers a tranquil retreat with its en-suite bath. Situated in close proximity to the 410/IH-10 interchange, this home ensures swift access to all that San Antonio has to offer. Whether it's work or leisure, you'll appreciate the ease of commuting and exploring the city. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a home in a prime location that embraces both comfort and connectivity. Schedule a viewing today!
